6.01	Peter_Jackson's_King_Kong_(video_game)	Peter Jackson's King Kong: The Official Game of the Movie	Peter Jackson's King Kong: The Official Game of the Movie is a first person shooter action adventure game based on the 2005 film King Kong. It is a collaboration between the film's director Peter Jackson and famed videogame designer Michel Ancel , remarkable in that such true cross-medium creative partnerships are rare in the realm of game development. It was released on PC and sixth generation platforms on November 17, 2005, as well as a mobile version also released in Winter 2005, developed by Gameloft. In the United States, the Game Boy Advance version is titled Kong: The 8th Wonder of the World. All film cast members reprise their roles.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/21/King-kong-cover-pc.jpg
